# Specs live in `agent-os/specs/`

This repository’s spec workflow stores specs under:

- `agent-os/specs/YYYY-MM-DD-kebab-case-spec-name/`

If you see links to `docs/specs/**` (e.g. in Linear issues), treat them as **potentially stale** for this repo/worktree and prefer creating/updating specs in `agent-os/specs/`.

